Welcome to NewYark!

A theme inspired by the tough, strong, yet elegant style of New York, New York.

**Includes**

* [Twitter Bootstrap 3.0 RC1](http://getbootstrap.com/)

* Reponsive design for mobile and tablets

* [Tags Page](http://http://tindrlabs.dev/tags)

**Installation**

* Download the themes zip or pull from Github

* Copy the NewYark folder over to the /public/themes directory of your WardrobeCMS site

* Goto /app/config/wardrobe.php and change the theme setting to 'theme' => 'newyark'

Hope you enjoy the theme. Questions or comments? Hit us up on Twitter [@tinderlabs](https://twitter.com/tindrlabs)